msgid ""
"Last anecdotal point, it was Bruce who was responsible for inspiring the "
"different “codenames” for Debian versions (1.1 — <emphasis "
"role=\"distribution\">Rex</emphasis>, 1.2 — <emphasis role=\"distribution\">"
"Buzz</emphasis>, 1.3 — <emphasis role=\"distribution\">Bo</emphasis>, 2.0 — <"
